{"tid":2338183,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港導演畫唔畫storyboard?","createTime":"2020-12-24T00:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T04:46:04.000Z","uid":384055,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"752d25c217fd7a2c3ef03ae602fd452a87f22f25","tid":2338183,"uid":384055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"有冇ching俾啲相尼睇下thx"},{"pid":"6f3361954335ef702e23d29f6d98d8997dc68687","tid":2338183,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"如果溫日良算係導演，咁佢有畫。<br />\n<br />\n由邵仲衡、趙碩之及陳蕊蕊等合演，漫畫家溫日良（肥良）執導的電影《母夜叉》，今日於尖沙嘴舉行首映。邵仲衡以為電影只在網上平台放映，估不到會登大銀幕。他指導演溫日良是漫畫家，首次執導演筒，拍攝手法與他過往接觸的傳統導演截然不同，「他寫劇本不是用文字表達，而是當畫漫畫咁寫，<span class=\"red\">未見過storyboard成本電話簿咁厚</span>&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n由呢句推斷都有其他導演畫，不過冇咁厚。"},{"pid":"0f0087521da49806d5dd4c6f1536ad7b4ff7dc46","tid":2338183,"uid":11185,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"老徐<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60200&amp;page=&amp;snA=19816&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60200%26page%3D%26snA%3D19816%26last%3D&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76Mc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=aea802f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60200&amp;page=&amp;snA=19816&amp;last=</a>"},{"pid":"cb6eb05f16c3ef8f854aae11a8748e1d58704b1c","tid":2338183,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"b0577b9b62eb567733a587934512bdebe49d50ec","tid":2338183,"uid":27597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"電影電視導演比較少畫<br />\n廣告就一定有storyboard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b9891032b3ec350ccb52723561b4553212a5b8","tid":2338183,"uid":384055,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0577b9b62eb567733a587934512bdebe49d50ec